{"tid":2202733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將對港旅警由「提高警覺」 提升至「三思而後行」","createTime":"2020-09-14T22:13:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T02:24:54.000Z","uid":24730,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"77af069f229f89e6bd086b31a62edaf73b2d4e6e","tid":2202733,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T22:13:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200915/XVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FXVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y%2F&d=B6Sv%2FagOPA3DZgijvYhacTYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=07579eab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200915%2FXVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y%2F&h=6b9bbfae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200915/XVNSOWHBLFDOTIHHUAY2RRQQ4Y/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院周一更新對香港的旅遊警示，因應武漢肺炎疫情及港版國安法，將對港旅警由第二級「提高警覺」（Exercise increased caution）提升至「三思而後行」（Reconsider travel）。"},{"pid":"4956534b6b15306c55411ea0961b2e3fd12a31b9","tid":2202733,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T22:15:23.000Z","msg":"美國國務院指出，因應武肺疫情與「任意執法」情況，國民到港前須三思。國務院在其網站提到，港版國安法7月1日生效之後，中國單方面任意在港行使警察與治安權，顯示其意圖運用權力針對「其所謂的分裂國安行為、顛覆、恐怖主義、『勾結』外國勢力」等廣泛活動，又指新法涵蓋非香港居民及香港以外機構的罪行，令公開批評中國的美國公民被捕、驅逐、起訴的風險增加，並指中國的「維護國家安全公署已在港運作」。網站並指中國發動文宣，誣捏一些人挑起社會動盪，某些情況下更公開他們的個人資料，令他們在社交網站受到恐嚇。...."},{"pid":"c6245062d5be1df546d51204a6f9b57e310fdbcf","tid":2202733,"uid":123774,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T22:17:18.000Z","msg":"唔知點解個腦彈左句解放軍「後果自負」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a440d31338d76fe8164d202735f4cc61b475d5ae","tid":2202733,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T22:53:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i